column5: oh lord there he is i promise not to horse him and will try to land him properly with my double oversized no hurt muskie net and my barbless hooks that  shall be seen in muskie heaven and please let the fish that i release live to spawn some more eaters for me to catch and also for the lil perch and the crappies bless this pan with butter and garlic amen!!!
Interesting Prayer! It's the new fishing prayer!
